        <terms:description>A physical embodiment of the Dataset in a particular format.</terms:description>
        <vann:usageNote>This represents a general availability of a dataset. It implies no information about the actual access method of the data, i.e., whether by direct download, API, or through a Web page. The use of dcat:downloadURL property indicates directly downloadable distributions.</vann:usageNote>
        <rdfs:subClassOf>dcat:Resource</rdfs:subClassOf>
